manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: JIMEIQI 6 Pocket Accordion File Organizer Tired of juggling between clipboards and folders? Look no further. Introducing the perfect solution to streamline your daily tasks - a clipboard and folder combined into one smart portfolio. Despite its compact 13" x 9.6" dimensions, this portfolio offers an abundance of storage space. As a clipboard, it’s firm, sturdy, and comfortable to write on. Yet, it is better than a standard clipboard because the pages are protected, and the cover provides privacy. Switch to folder mode, and you'll discover a range of Stay-put tabs that keep papers securely in place. The left pocket even boasts a clever die-cut business card slot, keeping your notes, papers, tags, mail, receipts, and business cards neatly organized.

Efficient Folder Design Transitioning to folder mode reveals an array of Stay-put tabs that effectively secure your documents in position. What's more, the left pocket features a nifty die-cut business card slot, ensuring impeccable organization for your notes, papers, tags, mail, receipts, and business cards High Quality Notebook This legal pad provides a tidy and accessible area for writing. It's an ideal choice for scribbling job interview queries, recording boardroom discussions, or capturing bursts of creativity for your next major marketing initiative. Moreover, it's highly useful for home improvement plans, managing tasks, or taking notes during classroom lectures at university Pen Pocket Unique pen pocket design, more convenient for you to record or modify files at any time Efficient Folder Design High Quality Notebook Pen Pocket

Q1: What are the dimensions of this accordion file organizer and its storage capacity? A1: This file organizer has dimensions of 13" x 9.25" and features 6 individual pockets, 1 legal pads , 1 main pocket, and 1 stay-put tab to prevent papers from falling out. Additionally, there is a die-cut business card slot in the left pocket with ample space. Q2: Can you describe the benefits of the upgraded snap button closure? A2: The upgraded snap button closure offers convenience with improved elastic buckles. It ensures effortless opening and closing of the folder, making your daily tasks smoother. Q3: Is this file organizer made from materials? A3: Yes, this file organizer is crafted from top-quality PP material. It's acid-free, PVC-free, and of archival quality, ensuring safe storage for your documents. Q4: How does this file organizer enhance organization and document management? A4: This 6 pocket accordion file folder is designed to upgrade your document organizer management. Its unique design allows you to store and classify letters/A4 files, receipts, and cards efficiently.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute, thin form factor, fastens shut, comes with a notepad
reviews.reviewText: I need a binder for taking notes but I wanted one with a thin form factor that would stay shut when I closed it. Ordinary ring binders wouldn't do, as they are too thick and don't stay closed, but this was great!Obviously if you fill it up with paper in the organizer section it will get bulkier but for general purposes note taking and organizing documents this is perfect. It's slim so it fits in my bag, I just have to be careful not to overstuff it.I was delighted that it actually came with a note pad! Ready to use right out of the box. I love the toothpaste mint color.
